          img(src="imgs/posterjam/poster-7.jpg" alt="screen printing activity")
          figcaption Figure A
        h6.ml-sect Figure A
        p.ml-sect To visually represent time,  I was inspired the British TV show Doctor Who where they travel through a luminous time vortex.  The layering of the arcs forces the viewer to read the text through 
